            "id": 415,
            "question_id": 139,
            "provider": "copilot-opus46",
            "locale": "en",
            "hint": "'But' highlights the contrast between a positive and a negative evaluation of the same experience.\nThe first part `food was great` is a positive verdict; `service was slow` is a negative one. Which conjunction contrasts positive and negative?",
